## Limitations

The findings are based on general cultural trends and may not account for individual or organizational variations within cultures. Additionally, the data is drawn from secondary sources, which may not reflect the most current research or account for recent changes in global business practices. Further empirical research could provide more nuanced insights into how these cultural perceptions are evolving in the context of globalization.